<span id="freeTextContainer8240760804988565250"><b>
  <u>19 Jun. &apos;20</u>
  <br/>
  <i>Not interested in providing a platform for dishonest debate, nor for people to spout alt-right talking points and obvious dog-whistling. I’m not gonna waste my time moderating this thread so consider this a warning for future commenters, I <u>will</u> indiscriminately remove comments, including future comments crying about the fact comments have been deleted. Go whine somewhere else.</i>
