<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1449354.Libido_Dominandi"><img alt="Libido Dominandi: Sexual Liberation and Political Control" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348227143l/1449354._SX98_.jpg" />
