<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer18347554509023893368">Jean Raspail was a French author, traveler and explorer. He was best known for his controversial 1973 novel, <i>The Camp of the Saints</i>, which is about mass third world immigration to Europe.</span>

</div>
